Article 1

Scope

This Regulation applies to the following issuers of asset referenced tokens and e-money tokens:

(a)   issuers of significant asset-referenced tokens;

(b)   electronic money institutions issuing significant e-money tokens;

(c)   issuers of asset-referenced tokens that are not significant, where required by a competent authority under

Article 35(4) of Regulation (EU) 2023/1114;

(d)   electronic money institutions issuing e-money tokens that are not significant, where required by a competent
            authority under Article 58(2) of Regulation (EU) 2023/1114.
